name: 凯琳·威尔金斯
name_full: 凯琳·威尔金斯 Kaelyn Wilkins
introduction: Kaelyn Wilkins is an American actress and Internet personality. Born in Houston, Texas - Kaelyn developed a love for being on camera and bringing people joy through her craft at a young age when she began creating content on YouTube. Since then, Kaelyn has amassed an audience of over 1.3 million viewers who loyally tune in content that she continues to create whilst she pursues her acting career.
